<!-- Modernized Privacy Policy Page -->
<section class="glass-card max-w-3xl mx-auto py-10 px-6 sm:px-12 rounded-3xl border border-primary/10 bg-white/70 backdrop-blur-xl shadow-lg space-y-6 leading-relaxed text-slate-600 my-8">
  <div class="text-center space-y-2 pb-4 border-b border-primary/10">
    <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1 bg-primary/10 rounded-full text-primary text-xs font-bold shadow-sm border border-primary/15">
      ⚖️ Legal & Security
    </span>
    <h1 class="font-headline text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-black text-slate-900 leading-tight">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 font-semibold">Last updated: June 20, 2026</p>
  </div>
  
  <p class="text-sm sm:text-base font-semibold text-slate-700">
    Welcome to <strong><%= appName %></strong>. We are committed to protecting your personal information and your wedding memories. This Privacy Policy describes how we collect, use, and safeguard your data when you use our platform.
  </p>

  <div class="space-y-4">
    <h2 class="font-headline text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800 border-b border-primary/5 pb-1">1. Information We Collect</h2>
    <p class="text-sm">We collect information in the following categories:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-5 text-sm space-y-1.5">
      <li><strong>Account Information:</strong> When couples register, we collect their name, email address, password hash, phone number, and Google ID (if Google Sign-In is used).</li>
      <li><strong>Event Details:</strong> Event titles, dates, venues, cities, and custom folder layouts.</li>
      <li><strong>Media Uploads:</strong> Photos and videos uploaded by guests. We automatically strip JPEG EXIF metadata (including GPS location data) upon upload to protect guest privacy.</li>
      <li><strong>Audit Logs:</strong> We log activity details (IP addresses, action names, timestamps) to monitor for security threats, fraud, or misuse.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="space-y-4">
    <h2 class="font-headline text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800 border-b border-primary/5 pb-1">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <p class="text-sm">We use the collected information to:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-5 text-sm space-y-1.5">
      <li>Provide, operate, and maintain the wedding memory collection platform.</li>
      <li>Authenticate users and enforce plan limits (storage limits, file sizes).</li>
      <li>Allow couples to moderate and manage guest uploads.</li>
      <li>Prevent duplicate file uploads using secure cryptographic hash checks (SHA-256).</li>
      <li>Secure the platform from spam using rate limits, IP blocklists, and CAPTCHAs.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="space-y-4">
    <h2 class="font-headline text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800 border-b border-primary/5 pb-1">3. Storage and Data Retention</h2>
    <p class="text-sm">
      All media uploaded to ShaadiShots is kept secure. Media files are stored either in a private directory on our local servers or inside secure cloud buckets (Amazon S3 or Cloudflare R2) depending on platform configuration. Media files are only public if the couple enables the public gallery. Deleted media files and deleted events are permanently removed from our active files immediately.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="space-y-4">
    <h2 class="font-headline text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800 border-b border-primary/5 pb-1">4. Sharing of Data</h2>
    <p class="text-sm">
      We do not sell, trade, or rent personal data or wedding media to third parties. Payments are securely processed through Razorpay; we do not store full credit card details or payment credentials on our servers.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="space-y-4">
    <h2 class="font-headline text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800 border-b border-primary/5 pb-1">5. Security Measures</h2>
    <p class="text-sm">
      We utilize multi-layer security protections including HTTPS, signed HTTP-only cookies, timing-safe CSRF checks, secure JWT verification, and Two-Factor Authentication (2FA) to ensure that only authorized owners can manage wedding content.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="space-y-4">
    <h2 class="font-headline text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800 border-b border-primary/5 pb-1">6. Your Rights</h2>
    <p class="text-sm">
      Couples and users have the right to edit their accounts, download their entire album as a ZIP file, or delete their events at any time. For questions regarding privacy or to request manual deletion of guest data, please submit a request on our <a href="/contact" class="text-primary font-bold hover:underline">Contact Page</a>.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="pt-6 border-t border-primary/10 text-center">
    <a href="/" class="border border-primary/20 bg-white hover:bg-slate-50 text-primary px-8 py-3 rounded-full font-bold text-sm shadow-sm transition-all inline-block">Back to Home</a>
  </div>
</section>
